Photo frame art is a decorative wall display that uses photo frames to showcase pictures, artwork, quotes, or memories in a stylish way. It is used to add a personal, elegant, and warm touch to any room. Photo frame art comes in many styles such as single frames, collage sets, family galleries, wooden frames, modern metallic frames, and custom designs. Frames also protect photos while improving their appearance.

Common Prices of Photo Frame Art (Pakistan)

Prices depend on size, material, and design:

Small frames: PKR 1,500 – 4,000
Medium sets: PKR 4,000 – 8,000
Large gallery / premium sets: PKR 8,000+
Where It Is Used
Living room wall
Bedroom wall
Stair wall
Hallway / entrance
Office desk or reception
Family gallery wall